{"tid":1431514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新口號] 身體健康","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:32:58.000Z","uid":259166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4f3742bf8476e433ee7aa1f41b711d5265b3cea0","tid":1431514,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"未輪到你。<br />\n<br />\n對住黑警，除左叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑社會</span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警可恥</span></span>，可以加多個新口號:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足口病</span></span><br />\n<br />\n根據世衞組織資料，手足口病係冇藥醫，同埋有好多死亡個案:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wpro.who.int/china/mediacentre/factsheets/hfmd/zh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wpro.who.int%2Fchina%2Fmediacentre%2Ffactsheets%2Fhfmd%2Fzh%2F&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=4eb67d76\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wpro.who.int/china/mediacentre/factsheets/hfmd/zh/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">对手足口病目前尚无特异性治疗</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">对引起手足口病的非脊髓灰质炎肠道病毒尚无特异性抗病毒药物或疫苗</span><br />\n<br />\n形势<br />\n<br />\n手足口病于2008年5月2日被列为国家监测系统的丙类法定传染病，要求对每一例病例都应在诊断后24小时内上报至国家法定传染病报告系统（NNDRS）。<br />\n<br />\n与肠道病毒71（EV71）有关的手足口病新发疫情令人严重关注。 <br />\n<br />\n2010年报告了约175万病例，其中包括905例<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死亡</span></span>；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n審判開始:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190807/s00001/1565186564787/%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%A3%E7%97%85%E6%95%B8%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85-%E8%A1%9B%E7%BD%B2%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%A5%E5%91%88%E5%A0%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190807%2Fs00001%2F1565186564787%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%2591%2588%25E5%25A0%25B1&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=21b56d1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190807%2Fs00001%2F1565186564787%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%2591%2588%25E5%25A0%25B1&h=3faf27de\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190807/s00001/1565186564787/%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%A3%E7%97%85%E6%95%B8%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85-%E8%A1%9B%E7%BD%B2%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%A5%E5%91%88%E5%A0%B1</a>"},{"pid":"900eb6be5d4d795311c00bd3d458ce2f2cb8a2f6","tid":1431514,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:19:26.000Z","msg":"手足口病"},{"pid":"04956e12b529ed477f36b17187ea2a29b5a4d2a8","tid":1431514,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"<code>手足口病</code>"},{"pid":"d121a62bcedabfe19757ef0bd581ffaf1c37662f","tid":1431514,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"<code>手足口病</code>"},{"pid":"ea483adc337d2b3bdee34a7173bf01b0217381d1","tid":1431514,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:22:42.000Z","msg":"<code>手足口病</code>"},{"pid":"5f16341ec4a5589e278b36d2fa9db762eae7c3c8","tid":1431514,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"<code>手足口病</code>"},{"pid":"fd3b0f50463f88eb5270aa87a1b296c7b5111173","tid":1431514,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7cb135341a7f7da424ca01bde5e29014807c67b","tid":1431514,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:32:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}